g.text:
You are a mushroom picker. Birds are going to interrupt
you. You can shoot them and pick as many mushrooms as possible in order to feed your wife. a: go left d: go right w: jump spacebar: shoot c-key: turn on cheat mode v-key: turn off cheat mode You must pick up all the mushroom before going back home. Besides, you can get double points in zoom mode which is harder.
